notes.title: Cleaning up
notes.detail: Need some questions answered about our car and vehicle auctions, but prefer to do it in person? We always love hearing from our Copart Members whether it’s a question about auction cars or salvage vehicles – or even questions about the other Texas Copart locations! Come meet our team at our Houston, TX location, Monday through Friday, between 8:00 a.m. and 5:00 p.m. And remember to thoroughly review Texas's licensing requirements so you're fully prepped and ready with all your necessary documents! We look forward to seeing you soon!
